---
---

<section id="approach" class="approach-section">
  <div class="approach-inner">
    <div class="approach-block approach-header fade-in stagger-1">
      <span class="approach-kicker">Approach</span>
    </div>

    <div class="approach-block fade-in stagger-2">
      <p class="approach-statement">
        I build software<br />
        that solves problems<br />
        without creating new ones.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="approach-rule"></div>

    <div class="approach-block fade-in stagger-3">
      <div class="approach-body">
        <p>
          I don't build software to use interesting technology. I build it to
          solve real problems. An app that helps riders maintain their
          motorcycles. A platform that replaces manual processes with
          integrated workflows. A website that communicates clearly and
          loads fast.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every decision is a tradeoff. The right database, the right level of
          abstraction, the right amount of code. I prefer code that's
          predictable — easy to understand, easy to change, and easy to
          trust. Code that's boring ships faster, breaks less, and lasts
          longer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="approach-rule"></div>

    <div class="approach-block fade-in stagger-4">
      <span class="principles-kicker">Principles</span>
      <div class="approach-principles">
        <div class="principle">
          <span class="principle-number">01</span>
          <p class="principle-text">Understand the problem.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle">
          <span class="principle-number">02</span>
          <p class="principle-text">Keep it simple.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle">
          <span class="principle-number">03</span>
          <p class="principle-text">Build to last.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .approach-section {
    background: #f7f6f3;
    padding: var(--space-11) 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .approach-inner {
    max-width: var(--content-wide);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-5);
  }

  .approach-block {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .approach-block:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .approach-header {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .approach-kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .approach-statement {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    max-width: 840px;
  }

  .approach-rule {
    width: 36px;
    height: 1px;
    background: #c8c6c0;
    margin: var(--space-10) 0;
  }

  .approach-body {
    max-width: var(--content-narrow);
  }

  .approach-body p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .approach-body p:first-child::first-letter {
    float: left;
    font-size: 3.5em;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 0.8;
    margin-right: 0.125em;
    padding-top: 0.05em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .approach-body p + p {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
  }

  .principles-kicker {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .approach-principles {
    max-width: var(--content-narrow);
  }

  .principle {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .principle:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .principle-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    width: 1.5em;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .principle-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 450;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .approach-section {
      padding: var(--space-9) 0;
    }

    .approach-block {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    }

    .approach-rule {
      margin: var(--space-8) 0;
    }

    .approach-statement {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 3rem);
    }

    .principle {
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }

    .principle-text {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
  }
</style>
